<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/365880-i-own-both-native-son-and-his-memoir">I own both &quot;Native Son&quot; and his memoir, &quot;Black Boy.&quot; Maybe this is a non-sequitur for a question due to the fact that it&#39;s all subjective, but I always appreciate an opinion or two.

Should I read &quot;Native Son&quot; first, or should I go ahead and start the memoir? What do you guys and gals think?</a>
</div>
