        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1204179821" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14994649265698583928">Maybe it&apos;s the inevitable melancholy of getting older, but reading this novel for the second time, roughly 13 years after the first go, has made me tremendously sad and despairing.<br/><br/>I would like to think the country is so much different 70 years after its publication, but is it?</span>
  <span id="freeText14994649265698583928" style="display:none">Maybe it's the inevitable melancholy of getting older, but reading this novel for the second time, roughly 13 years after the first go, has made me tremendously sad and despairing.<br /><br />I would like to think the country is so much different 70 years after its publication, but is it?</span>
